title: Statistics Lithuania will cooperate with Vytautas Magnus University (Statistics Lithuania)
text: ( Source : Statistics Lithuania ) On 13 October , Statistics Lithuania and Vytautas Magnus University signed an agreement on cooperation in the scientific, educational and social partnership areas: preparation and implementation of research,
